          "content": "$8^{\\frac{2}{3}}\\times\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)^{-1}\\times\\left(\\log_9 3+3^{\\log_3 1}\\right)\\times2\\sin\\frac{\\pi}{6}$의 값은? [4점]",
